{"tid":2232022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙螺獨立 和你封關 Day 7","createTime":"2020-10-06T05:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T09:24:08.000Z","uid":186,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d76e57f9581cf453a9b6f446e3083a4396b4cf5c","tid":2232022,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:52:59.000Z","msg":"2020年9月30日再度封村，封鎖入村的鐵閘，告示聲稱2014年已經開始封村，但受到部份旅遊人士攻擊，危害村民生命及財產安全，因此<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>禁止非沙螺灣村居民和所有政府部門及公營機構進入沙螺灣村範圍，否則被視為盜賊。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人 中國人不准進入<br />\n沙螺灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙螺獨立後 第七日<br />\n政府一句聲都唔敢出"},{"pid":"7c6478ab9fe7fb30e4b63aed00c062707ce8b899","tid":2232022,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"繼續關注 獨立派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9edb87a3b004d577a889bcfe0915226af4db30","tid":2232022,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"沙螺人 站出來"},{"pid":"b0e16d59b506c9679cb3c4bc073bfa5c016b414d","tid":2232022,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"估唔到國中國可以係中國見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fc5dd217e1813b88b80ebe5e627e73e2037eaa","tid":2232022,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0e16d59b506c9679cb3c4bc073bfa5c016b414d","tid":2232022,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"估唔到國中國可以係中國見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"已經一個星期啦<br />\n有地勢保護"},{"pid":"d4ab7e7bd4f6dba53f767997b0bed36cfdf3a57e","tid":2232022,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"國安法個堆人去左邊?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c2877694439c5fd20a7148b288a99d6fa33684","tid":2232022,"uid":81756,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:58:20.000Z","msg":"支持村民班連燈撚呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1190895447687661/posts/3127300317380488/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1190895447687661%2Fposts%2F3127300317380488%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=b321d1f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1190895447687661/posts/3127300317380488/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n沙螺灣的如意算盤<br />\n<br />\n好一段時間沒行過東大古道，昨日驚見沙螺灣首次出現汽車！而且不只一兩架。原來有人私自擴闊村路，削走山坡，砍去樹木，斬斷樹根，形成一條可行車的路，接駁到深石村的馬路，可經深屈道出嶼南路和東涌。奇怪在一直未見報道，環團跟進，或山界討論。<br />\n<br />\n沙螺灣村一直要求政府興建馬路是人所共知，奈何由於人口稀少，位置偏僻而不符現行政策。現時村民出入可靠渡輪(去東涌+屯門)或機車(去深屈)，作為退休或過田園生活之地，基本生活需要不成問題。但有了馬路之後土地就能升價百倍，可申建丁屋轉售，自然有鄉紳策劃私自開墾車路，而封村亦是迫使政府將車路合法化的手段之一。有人估計，政府評估興建馬路的其中一個指標是緊急召喚的次數，封村造成和行山人士衝突，增加報警次數有助達標。<br />\n<br />\n如果村民只求樸素的鄉郊生活，沙螺灣本來已經是一個好地方，可耕種，可釣魚。這條村亦享受了大量公帑支助，有公廁，有球場，有政府建的行人路，有街燈，有食環署收集垃圾和路旁剪草，單是一個渡輪碼頭的建造費用已超過這些村民一生所納的税！他們享受了香港納稅人的支助，毫不感恩，卻僭建鐵閘，把公家路封起來，並威嚇過路的行山人士，只會令社會更加反感。<br />\n<br />\n面對這種貪得無厭的沙螺灣人，一種回應方法是抵制，陰乾他們，令隔離深屈村、䃟頭村經營士多的村民也憎厭他們。另一種回應是更關注非法開路，責成地政署豎立鐵柱阻止車輛出入，並反對任何將它變為合法馬路的企圖，睇實政府不可鬆章。希望環團能積極跟進此事，並追究大削山坡所造成的生態破壞。"},{"pid":"c1f669e18153556fe83ea20d08e30c1ddfe6bb2a","tid":2232022,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee9edb87a3b004d577a889bcfe0915226af4db30","tid":2232022,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"沙螺人 站出來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"英雄名嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb72e080a27f860ff356e039e9906902e2859cc","tid":2232022,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"支持沙螺獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df808d37ed4d6a90775564a3102519357a1bc51c","tid":2232022,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:07:01.000Z","msg":"話說佢地有冇封埋個碼頭"},{"pid":"53178b38fd468888cd469987a5c17136fe3390ea","tid":2232022,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"終於有一部分香港土地獨立成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後要建軍 擴佔領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082e557431cd058bd817488202381ad05cee706e","tid":2232022,"uid":271199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"沙螺獨立 唯一出路<br />\n沙螺建國 民族自強"},{"pid":"76f001f5228024ac23da834c70b01691c3bde37a","tid":2232022,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4ab7e7bd4f6dba53f767997b0bed36cfdf3a57e","tid":2232022,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"國安法個堆人去左邊?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"李桂華大導演都怕左鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58812e97d247ff86e12b9f1f526eb0c79b3eb822","tid":2232022,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"沙螺國成立<br />\n以後過去要拎visa"},{"pid":"8fb22faa40e82e5a5fefe4c4bb6bd2a139a161b8","tid":2232022,"uid":261522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl